premise_source_doc_sentence: Michael Anthony Trevino  (  born January 25 , 1985  )  is an American actor .
He is known for his role as Tyler Lockwood in The CW 's series The Vampire Diaries .
Michael Trevino has won the Choice TV Male Scene Stealer award for two consecutive years -- 2011 and 2012 -- for his role of Tyler Lockwood , a vampire-werewolf hybrid .
Tyler Lockwood 's  (  Michael Trevino  )  uncle , Mason Lockwood  (  Taylor Kinney  )  , arrives in town searching for the moonstone , a family heirloom .
On April 6 , 2015 , lead actress Nina Dobrev confirmed via Instagram that she and co-star Michael Trevino  (  who plays Tyler Lockwood  )  would be leaving the show after its sixth season .
